OL,3,CDisruption warning as Scottish Water
OL,4,Cstaff begin two-day strike at midnight
OL,6,FScottish Water staff will stage a two-
OL,7,Fday strike from midnight amid a
OL,8,Fcontinued dispute over pay.
OL,10,FWorkers will walk out on Tuesday and
OL,11,FWednesday following a one-day strike
OL,12,Flast month.
OL,14,FUnison, which represents more than
OL,15,F1,000 staff, warned that emergency
OL,16,Frepairs and water quality checks will
OL,17,Fnot be carried out during that time.
