OL,3,CDisruption warning as Scottish Water
OL,4,Cstaff begin two-day strike at midnight
OL,6,FUnison Scotland regional organiser
OL,7,FEmma Phillips said: "Strike action is
OL,8,Falways a last resort.
OL,10,F"Staff have suffered a decade of pay
OL,11,Fdeals that haven't kept up with
OL,12,Finflation.
OL,14,F"They are not willing to be underpaid
OL,15,Fany longer.
OL,17,F"The union has done everything it can
OL,18,Fto try and get Scottish Water's senior
OL,19,Fmanagers to put a fair offer on the
OL,20,Ftable, but they are refusing to be
OL,21,Freasonable."
