OL,6,FUnison Scottish Water branch secretary
OL,7,FTricia McArthur added: "Scottish Water
OL,8,Fworkers are simply asking to be paid
OL,9,Ffairly for the essential services upon
OL,10,Fwhich everyone in Scotland relies.
OL,12,F"Things are meant to be different in a
OL,13,Fpublicly owned service like this.
OL,15,F"But senior managers are behaving no
OL,16,Fdifferently to those running private
OL,17,Fwater companies south of the border."
