OL,6,FPeter Farrer, Scottish Water's chief
OL,7,Foperating officer, said: "No-one
OL,8,Fbenefits from industrial action, and
OL,9,Four focus is on continuing to deliver
OL,10,Ffor our millions of customers across
OL,11,FScotland.
OL,13,F"Our above-inflation pay proposal is
OL,14,Ffair and progressive, prioritising the
OL,15,Fhighest percentage increases in the
OL,16,Fbusiness for those on the lowest
OL,17,Fsalary grades ` money that should be
OL,18,Fin employees' pockets now.
