OL,6,F"We met with Acas and the trade unions
OL,7,Fon April 15 to explore options to
OL,8,Fresolve the current dispute. Following
OL,9,Fthat, we made a different, further
OL,10,Fimproved proposal in an effort to
OL,11,Freach an agreement.
OL,13,F"This is a good proposal, and we are
OL,14,Fdisappointed that union officials have
OL,15,Fnot shared it with their members and
OL,16,Fgiven them the opportunity to vote on
OL,17,Fthe offer in a ballot.
OL,19,F"We urge the unions to get back round
OL,20,Fthe negotiating table as soon as
OL,21,Fpossible."
